<subSubSection id="C32B2BD6BF536A07FF3EFD43C33FFC50" pageId="3" pageNumber="69" type="diagnosis">
<paragraph id="8B8E785DBF536A07FF3EFD43C699FD5C" blockId="3.[136,251,640,666]" box="[136,251,640,666]" pageId="3" pageNumber="69">
<heading id="D0C6CF31BF536A07FF3EFD43C699FD5C" bold="true" box="[136,251,640,666]" fontSize="11" level="1" pageId="3" pageNumber="69" reason="1">
<emphasis id="B945A44FBF536A07FF3EFD43C699FD5C" bold="true" box="[136,251,640,666]" pageId="3" pageNumber="69">Diagnosis</emphasis>
</heading>
</paragraph>
<paragraph id="8B8E785DBF536A07FF3EFD0BC33FFC50" blockId="3.[136,1451,712,918]" pageId="3" pageNumber="69">
<taxonomicName id="4C3103DEBF536A07FF3EFD0BC69FFD24" authorityName="A. A. Khuroo, K. Hussain &amp; R. Gulzar" authorityYear="2022" baseAuthorityName="A. A. Khuroo, K. Hussain &amp; R. Gulzar" baseAuthorityYear="2022" box="[136,253,712,738]" class="Magnoliopsida" family="Rosaceae" genus="Geum" kingdom="Plantae" order="Rosales" pageId="3" pageNumber="69" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="species" species="rubrum">
<emphasis id="B945A44FBF536A07FF3EFD0BC69FFD24" box="[136,253,712,738]" italics="true" pageId="3" pageNumber="69">G. rubrum</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
resembles with 
<taxonomicName id="4C3103DEBF536A07FE18FD0BC479FD24" box="[430,539,712,738]" class="Magnoliopsida" family="Rosaceae" genus="Geum" kingdom="Plantae" order="Rosales" pageId="3" pageNumber="69" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="species" species="elatum">
<emphasis id="B945A44FBF536A07FE18FD0BC479FD24" box="[430,539,712,738]" italics="true" pageId="3" pageNumber="69">G. elatum</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
in few characters, such as shape of basal leaves and stem. However, 
<taxonomicName id="4C3103DEBF536A07FABDFD0BC31DFD24" authorityName="A. A. Khuroo, K. Hussain &amp; R. Gulzar" authorityYear="2022" baseAuthorityName="A. A. Khuroo, K. Hussain &amp; R. Gulzar" baseAuthorityYear="2022" box="[1291,1407,712,738]" class="Magnoliopsida" family="Rosaceae" genus="Geum" kingdom="Plantae" order="Rosales" pageId="3" pageNumber="69" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="species" species="rubrum">
<emphasis id="B945A44FBF536A07FABDFD0BC31DFD24" box="[1291,1407,712,738]" italics="true" pageId="3" pageNumber="69">G. rubrum</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
can be clearly distinguished from 
<taxonomicName id="4C3103DEBF536A07FE6CFD2FC42BFCC0" box="[474,585,748,774]" class="Magnoliopsida" family="Rosaceae" genus="Geum" kingdom="Plantae" order="Rosales" pageId="3" pageNumber="69" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="species" species="elatum">
<emphasis id="B945A44FBF536A07FE6CFD2FC42BFCC0" box="[474,585,748,774]" italics="true" pageId="3" pageNumber="69">G. elatum</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
on the basis of several distinctive characters which include: flower diameter (
<quantity id="4CC9D5B8BF536A07FF26FCD3C76CFCED" box="[144,270,784,811]" metricMagnitude="-2" metricUnit="m" metricValue="2.5" metricValueMax="2.8" metricValueMin="2.2" pageId="3" pageNumber="69" unit="cm" value="2.5" valueMax="2.8" valueMin="2.2">2.2–2.8 cm</quantity>
in 
<taxonomicName id="4C3103DEBF536A07FE86FCD3C7C4FCEC" authorityName="A. A. Khuroo, K. Hussain &amp; R. Gulzar" authorityYear="2022" baseAuthorityName="A. A. Khuroo, K. Hussain &amp; R. Gulzar" baseAuthorityYear="2022" box="[304,422,784,810]" class="Magnoliopsida" family="Rosaceae" genus="Geum" kingdom="Plantae" order="Rosales" pageId="3" pageNumber="69" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="species" species="rubrum">
<emphasis id="B945A44FBF536A07FE86FCD3C7C4FCEC" box="[304,422,784,810]" italics="true" pageId="3" pageNumber="69">G. rubrum</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
vs. 3.0– 
<quantity id="4CC9D5B8BF536A07FDB2FCD3C42CFCED" box="[516,590,784,811]" metricMagnitude="-2" metricUnit="m" metricValue="3.5" pageId="3" pageNumber="69" unit="cm" value="3.5">3.5 cm</quantity>
in 
<taxonomicName id="4C3103DEBF536A07FDC7FCD3C4BCFCEC" box="[625,734,784,810]" class="Magnoliopsida" family="Rosaceae" genus="Geum" kingdom="Plantae" order="Rosales" pageId="3" pageNumber="69" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="species" species="elatum">
<emphasis id="B945A44FBF536A07FDC7FCD3C4BCFCEC" box="[625,734,784,810]" italics="true" pageId="3" pageNumber="69">G. elatum</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
), shape of pseudo-sepal (elliptic or lanceolate vs. ovate), 
<typeStatus id="548AC6FFBF536A07FAEBFCD2C3EFFCED" box="[1373,1421,785,811]" pageId="3" pageNumber="69">type</typeStatus>
of hairs on calyx (glandular vs. aglandular), color of petals (red vs. yellow), anther attachment (dorsifixed vs. basifixed), number of carpels (6–8 vs. 10–24) and achene size (7.8–8.0 × 
<quantity id="4CC9D5B8BF536A07FC8CFC9BC5A0FCB5" box="[826,962,856,883]" metricMagnitude="-3" metricUnit="m" metricValue="1.7" metricValueMax="1.8" metricValueMin="1.6" pageId="3" pageNumber="69" unit="mm" value="1.7" valueMax="1.8" valueMin="1.6">1.6–1.8 mm</quantity>
vs. 3.7–3.9 × 
<quantity id="4CC9D5B8BF536A07FBD6FC9BC28AFCB5" box="[1120,1256,856,883]" metricMagnitude="-3" metricUnit="m" metricValue="1.0" metricValueMax="1.1" metricValueMin="0.9" pageId="3" pageNumber="69" unit="mm" value="1.0" valueMax="1.1" valueMin="0.9">0.9–1.1 mm</quantity>
) (
<figureCitation id="130A64D8BF536A07FB49FC9BC30BFCB4" box="[1279,1385,856,882]" captionStart="FIGURE 2" captionStartId="2.[136,229,1538,1560]" captionTargetBox="[352,1238,190,1514]" captionTargetId="figure-19@2.[349,1238,190,1514]" captionTargetPageId="2" captionText="FIGURE 2. Geum rubrum. A. Habit; B. Flower; C. Sepal; D. Petal; E. Stamen (2x); F. Carpels (2x); G. Achene." figureDoi="http://doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.6375243" httpUri="https://zenodo.org/record/6375243/files/figure.png" pageId="3" pageNumber="69">Figures 2</figureCitation>
&amp; 
<figureCitation id="130A64D8BF536A07FA3BFC9BC3F9FCB4" box="[1421,1435,856,882]" captionStart="FIGURE 3" captionStartId="4.[136,229,2017,2039]" captionTargetBox="[295,1293,613,1992]" captionTargetId="figure-122@4.[295,1293,497,1992]" captionTargetPageId="4" captionText="FIGURE 3. Geum elatum. A. Habit; B. Flower; C. Sepal; D. Petal (2x); E. Stamen (2x); F. Carpels (2x); G. Achene." figureDoi="http://doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.6375247" httpUri="https://zenodo.org/record/6375247/files/figure.png" pageId="3" pageNumber="69">3</figureCitation>
<emphasis id="B945A44FBF536A07FA2DFC9BC3C6FCB4" bold="true" box="[1435,1444,856,882]" pageId="3" pageNumber="69">)</emphasis>
. 
<collectionCode id="ED20E098BF536A07FF3EFCBFC6F9FC50" box="[136,155,892,918]" country="USA" lsid="urn:lsid:biocol.org:col:15406" name="Harvard University - Arnold Arboretum" pageId="3" pageNumber="69" type="Herbarium">A</collectionCode>
detailed comparison of these delimiting characters between 
<taxonomicName id="4C3103DEBF536A07FCF7FCBFC5D5FC50" authorityName="A. A. Khuroo, K. Hussain &amp; R. Gulzar" authorityYear="2022" baseAuthorityName="A. A. Khuroo, K. Hussain &amp; R. Gulzar" baseAuthorityYear="2022" box="[833,951,892,918]" class="Magnoliopsida" family="Rosaceae" genus="Geum" kingdom="Plantae" order="Rosales" pageId="3" pageNumber="69" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="species" species="rubrum">
<emphasis id="B945A44FBF536A07FCF7FCBFC5D5FC50" box="[833,951,892,918]" italics="true" pageId="3" pageNumber="69">G. rubrum</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
and 
<taxonomicName id="4C3103DEBF536A07FC5BFCBFC23EFC50" box="[1005,1116,892,918]" class="Magnoliopsida" family="Rosaceae" genus="Geum" kingdom="Plantae" order="Rosales" pageId="3" pageNumber="69" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="species" species="elatum">
<emphasis id="B945A44FBF536A07FC5BFCBFC23EFC50" box="[1005,1116,892,918]" italics="true" pageId="3" pageNumber="69">G. elatum</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
is provided in 
<tableCitation id="C6B34DE6BF536A07FAB5FCBFC335FC50" box="[1283,1367,892,918]" captionStart="TABLE 1" captionStartId="3.[136,224,966,990]" captionTargetPageId="3" captionText="TABLE 1. Comparison of distinguishing characters between Geum rubrum and Geum elatum." httpUri="http://table.plazi.org/id/DF4E28D5BF536A07FF3EFC05C21AFC18" pageId="3" pageNumber="69" tableUuid="DF4E28D5BF536A07FF3EFC05C21AFC18">Table 1</tableCitation>
.
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
<caption id="DF4E28D5BF536A07FF3EFC05C21AFC18" ID-Table-UUID="DF4E28D5BF536A07FF3EFC05C21AFC18" box="[136,1144,966,990]" httpUri="http://table.plazi.org/id/DF4E28D5BF536A07FF3EFC05C21AFC18" pageId="3" pageNumber="69" startId="3.[136,224,966,990]" targetBox="[144,1230,1027,1654]" targetIsTable="true" targetPageId="3">
<paragraph id="8B8E785DBF536A07FF3EFC05C21AFC18" blockId="3.[136,1144,966,990]" box="[136,1144,966,990]" pageId="3" pageNumber="69">
<emphasis id="B945A44FBF536A07FF3EFC05C699FC18" bold="true" box="[136,251,966,990]" pageId="3" pageNumber="69">TABLE 1.</emphasis>
Comparison of distinguishing characters between 
<taxonomicName id="4C3103DEBF536A07FCAEFC05C5CCFC18" authorityName="A. A. Khuroo, K. Hussain &amp; R. Gulzar" authorityYear="2022" baseAuthorityName="A. A. Khuroo, K. Hussain &amp; R. Gulzar" baseAuthorityYear="2022" box="[792,942,966,990]" class="Magnoliopsida" family="Rosaceae" genus="Geum" kingdom="Plantae" order="Rosales" pageId="3" pageNumber="69" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="species" species="rubrum">
<emphasis id="B945A44FBF536A07FCAEFC05C5CCFC18" box="[792,942,966,990]" italics="true" pageId="3" pageNumber="69">Geum rubrum</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
and 
<taxonomicName id="4C3103DEBF536A07FC54FC05C216FC18" box="[994,1140,966,990]" class="Magnoliopsida" family="Rosaceae" genus="Geum" kingdom="Plantae" order="Rosales" pageId="3" pageNumber="69" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="species" species="elatum">Geum elatum</taxonomicName>
.
